long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Pro Se automatically reads and analyses online privacy policies on your behalf.

It empowers you to make informed decisions about your privacy rights. Pro Se provides analysis reports including: what data is being collected and by whom, for what purpose, how long is data being kept, what is a legal basis for data collection. Pro Se will also inform you about your data protection rights (right to access, rectify, delete, and port your data, right to opt out and provide/withdraw consent) as well as what security measures are applied to protect your data.

Pro Se features an AI powered chat bot which can provide you with answers to any question you might have about data and privacy protection practices presented in a privacy policy text.
